  "short_description": "Let's solve artists' dilemmas while solving 3D puzzles using optical illusions. Paint the canvas with crayons, erase with an eraser, turn the wheels, and change the camera perspective. To create a perfect piece, you must use all art materials to color every square of the canvas.",
