  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Spready</i>, solve unique 3D puzzles with optical illusions to guide artists through their challenges and conflicts as they bring artworks to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The essence of artists' lives and journeys lies within the paintings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To create a perfect piece, you must utilize various gimmicks to color every inch of the canvas without leaving any gaps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Crayon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/b3bef0031c53fe7909c6d0b0b844c89e.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/b3bef0031c53fe7909c6d0b0b844c89e.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/b3bef0031c53fe7909c6d0b0b844c89e.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the crayons placed on the canvas. You can color the canvas! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bent canvas & Eraser</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/e1543faa9f28c295e84b6ea2e95e2163.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/e1543faa9f28c295e84b6ea2e95e2163.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/e1543faa9f28c295e84b6ea2e95e2163.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abandon the bias that the canvas is flat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even a bent canvas can be colored as much as you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And try using an eraser on the parts you want to erase!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wheel</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/116a43b521b3c0febcad0f97f8b42763.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/116a43b521b3c0febcad0f97f8b42763.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/116a43b521b3c0febcad0f97f8b42763.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have a bent canvas, there's also a rotating canvas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use wheels to freely rotate the canvas while coloring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Duplicate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/d2b12d3de31c8c9eeba6683767f4ce03.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/d2b12d3de31c8c9eeba6683767f4ce03.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/d2b12d3de31c8c9eeba6683767f4ce03.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What will happen when you overlap canvases behind other canvases?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try duplicating crayons ans erasers to fill in any missing parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Optical illusion Connection</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/cf7b8d6f9a2a600ebc732abe3cf3cb03.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/cf7b8d6f9a2a600ebc732abe3cf3cb03.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/cf7b8d6f9a2a600ebc732abe3cf3cb03.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use optical illusions to move the crayon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll be able to color canvases that are far away.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Spready</i>, solve unique 3D puzzles with optical illusions to guide artists through their challenges and conflicts as they bring artworks to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The essence of artists' lives and journeys lies within the paintings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To create a perfect piece, you must utilize various gimmicks to color every inch of the canvas without leaving any gaps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Crayon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/b3bef0031c53fe7909c6d0b0b844c89e.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/b3bef0031c53fe7909c6d0b0b844c89e.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/b3bef0031c53fe7909c6d0b0b844c89e.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the crayons placed on the canvas. You can color the canvas! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bent canvas & Eraser</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/e1543faa9f28c295e84b6ea2e95e2163.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/e1543faa9f28c295e84b6ea2e95e2163.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/e1543faa9f28c295e84b6ea2e95e2163.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abandon the bias that the canvas is flat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even a bent canvas can be colored as much as you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And try using an eraser on the parts you want to erase!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wheel</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/116a43b521b3c0febcad0f97f8b42763.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/116a43b521b3c0febcad0f97f8b42763.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/116a43b521b3c0febcad0f97f8b42763.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have a bent canvas, there's also a rotating canvas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use wheels to freely rotate the canvas while coloring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Duplicate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/d2b12d3de31c8c9eeba6683767f4ce03.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/d2b12d3de31c8c9eeba6683767f4ce03.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/d2b12d3de31c8c9eeba6683767f4ce03.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What will happen when you overlap canvases behind other canvases?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try duplicating crayons ans erasers to fill in any missing parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Optical illusion Connection</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/cf7b8d6f9a2a600ebc732abe3cf3cb03.poster.avif?t=1763227311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/cf7b8d6f9a2a600ebc732abe3cf3cb03.webm?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/cf7b8d6f9a2a600ebc732abe3cf3cb03.mp4?t=1763227311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use optical illusions to move the crayon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll be able to color canvases that are far away.</p>",
